STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jesse Thomas GRAHAM. No. 515P97-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Jesse Thomas Graham, Pro Se. Anne M. Middleton, Assistant Attorney General, R. Stuart Albright, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 3rd day of January 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
